articles.description: Ty Taylor II had 19 points and Devontae Cacok added 17 with 21 rebounds as UNC Wilmington got off to a fast start and easily defeated Elon 87-63 on Thursday night.
articles.headline: Taylor, Cacok lead UNC Wilmington to 87-63 win over Elon

articles.description: Sterling Taplin scored a career-high 30 points and Tulsa beat UConn 73-71, sweeping the season series from the Huskies.

articles.headline: Fairleigh Dickinson knocks off Mount St. Mary's, 80-79
